hadiths[23]{hadithnumber,text}:
4140,"Hazrat Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : musalman kaafir ka waaris nahi banta, na kaafir musalman ka waaris banta hai."
4141,"Wuhaib ne hamein ibne-Taaus se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : muqarrara hissey haqdaaron ko 2 aur jo bach jaey wo sabse qaribi rishta rakhney waley mard ke liye hai."
4142,"Rooh bin-Qasim ne baqi bachi pichhli sanad ke sath Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : muqarrara hissey unke haqdaaron ko 2 aur unse jo baqi bachchey wo sabse qaribi mard ka hai."
4143,Mamar ne hamein ibne- Taaus se baqi bachi pichhli sanad se riwayat ki : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maal ko Allah ki kitab ki ro se muqarrar karda hissey walon ke darmyan taqseem karo aur jo un hisson se bach jaey wo sabse qaribi mard ke liye hai.
4144,Yahya bin Ayub ne ibne- Taaus se isi sanad ke sath Wuhaib aur Rooh bin-Qasim ki hadis ke ham-mana riwayat bayan ki.
4145,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne hamein Muhammad-bin Munkadir se hadis bayan ki : unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne kaha : main bimar hua to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) meri iyaadat karne ke liye paidal chal kar tashrif laaey, mujh par ghashi ho gaee to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wuzu kya, phir apne wuzu ka pani mujh par daala to mujhey fayda ho gaya, maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! main apne maal ke barey mein kaisey faisla karun? (usko aisey hi chhod jaun ya wasiiyat karun wasiyat karun to kitney hissey mein? us waqt Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ke walid zinda they na aur koi beta tha.) aap ne mujhey jawab na diya yahan tak ke wiraasat ki aayat nazil hui : wo aap se fatwa maangtey hain, keh dijiye : Allah tumhen kalaala ke barey mein fatwa deta hai."
4146,"ibne-Juraij ne hamein hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey ibne-Munkadir ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne banu-Salma (ke ilaaqey ( mein paidal chal kar meri iyaadat ki, aap ne mujhey us haalat mein paya ke main kuchh samajh nahi pa raha tha, aap ne pani mangwaya, wuzu kya, phir usmein se mujh par chheentey maarey to mujhey fayda ho gaya, maine kaha : Allah ke rasool! main apne maal mein kya karun? to (ye aayat ( nazil hui : Allah tumhen tumhari aulad ke barey mein taakeedi hukm deta hai, mard ke liye 2 aurton ke hissey ke barabar hai."
4147,"Sufiyan ( Sory ( ne hamein hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Muhammad-bin-Munkadir se suna, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : main bimar tha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne meri iyaadat ki, aap ke sath Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they, donon paidal chal kar tashrif laey. aap ne mujhey (is haalat mein) paya ke mujh par ghashi taari thi, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wuzu kiya, phir apne wuzu ka bacha hua pani mujh par daala , main hosh mein aa gaya to dekha samney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif farma hain. maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool ! main apne maal ke barey mein kya karun? kaha : aap ne mujhey koi jawab na diya yahan tak ke wiraasat ki aayat nazil hui."
4148,"Ba'haz ne hamein hadis bayan ki : Shoba ne hamein hadis bayan ki : mujhey Muhammad-bin-Munkadir ne khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere yahan tashrif laey jabke mein bimar tha aur be-hosh tha. aap ne wuzu kiya to logon ne aap ke wuzu ka bacha hua pani mujh par daala , (us par) mujhey fayda hua to maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool ! mera waaris kalaala banega . (us waqt Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ki bahnein hi thin jo waaris banti thin) is par wiraasat ki aayat nazil hui. maine Muhammad-bin Munkadir se puchha : kalaala (يَسْتَفْتُونَكَ قُلِ اللَّهُ يُفْتِيكُمْ فِي الْكَلَالَةِ ) ( wali aayat )? unhon-ne kaha : isi tarah (Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ke sawal par) nazil ki gaee."
4149,"Nazar-bin-Shumail , abu-Aamir aqadi aur Wahab-bin-Jareer sab ne Shoba se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, Wahab-bin-Jareer ki hadis mein hai : to aayat faraaiz nazil hui aur unmein se kisi ki hadis mein ibne-Munkadir se Shoba ke sawal ka tazkira nahi hai."
4150,"Hisham ne hamein hadis bayan ki : hamein Qatada ne Saalim-bin abi Jaad se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Madaan bin abi Talha se riwayat ki ke Hazrat umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne Juma ke din khutba diya, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka tazkira kya aur Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ka tazkira kya, phir kaha : main apne baad koi aisi cheez nahi chhod raha jo mere yahan kalaala se zyada aham ho, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kisi cheez ke barey mein itni maraajiat nahi ki jitni kalaala ke barey mein ki, aur aap ne bhi mujh se kisi cheez ke barey mein itni shiddat ikhtiyar nahi farmai jitni kalaala ke barey mein farmai yahan tak ke aap ne apni ungli mere seeney mein chubhoi aur farmaya : aey umr ! tumhen mausam garma (mein nazil honey) wali aayat kafi nahi jo sura Nisa ke aakhir mein hai? (jis se masla waazeh ho gaya hai) aur main ( umr ( agar zinda raha to iske barey mein aisa waazeh faisla karunga jis (ko dekhtey huey) aisa shakhs ( bhi) faisla kar sakega jo Quran padhta (aur samajhta ( hai aur wo bhi jo Quran nahi padhta ."
4151,Saeed-bin-abi-Aruba aur Shoba donon ne Qatada se isi sanad ke sath usi ke ham mana hadis bayan ki.
4152,"ibne-abi-Khalid ne Abu-Ishaq se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Bara (bin Aazib ( (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Quran ki aakhiri aayat jo nazil hui (ye thi) ( يَسْتَفْتُونَكَ قُلِ اللَّهُ يُفْتِيكُمْ فِي الْكَلَالَةِ ( wo aap se fatwa maangtey hain, keh dijiye : Allah tumhen kalaala ke barey mein fatwa deta hai."
4153,"Shoba ne hamein Abu-Ishaq se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : aakhiri aayat jo nazil ki gaee, aayat kalaala hai aur aakhiri sura jo nazil ki gaee, sura baraat hai. ( sura tauba ka doosra naam , sura baraat hai.)"
4154,"Zakariya ne hamein Abu-Ishaq ke waastey se Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki ke aakhiri sura jo poori nazil ki gaee, sura tauba hai aur aakhiri aayat jo nazil ki gaee, aayat kalaala hai."
4155,Ammar bin Ruzeq ne hamein Abu-Ishaq ke hawale se Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) se usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki magar unhon-ne kaha : aakhiri sura jo mukammal nazil ki gaee. (taamma) ke bajaey ( كاملۃ (ke alfaz hain.)
4156,"abu-Safar ne Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : aakhiri aayat jo utari gaee, ( يَسْتَفْتُونَكَ ( hai."
4157,"Yunus ne mujhey ibne-Shahab se khabar di, unhon-ne abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas kisi ( aisey ( shakhs ki maiyat laai jati jis par qarz hota to aap poochhtey : kya usne qarz ki adaaeygi ke liye kuchh chhoda hai? agar bataya jata ke usne qarz chukaaney ke baqadr maal chhoda hai to aap uski namaze-janaza padha detey warna farmatey : apne sathi ki namaze-janaza padho. jab Allah ne aap par futoohaat ke darwazey kholey to aap ne farmaya : main mominon ke khud unki nisbat zyada qareeb hon, to jo shakhs faut ho jaey aur is par qarz ho uski adaaeygi mere zimmey hai aur jo maal chhod jaey wo iske waarison ka hai."
4158,"aqeel, ibne-Shahab (Zohri) ke bhatijey aur ibne-abi-Ze-ib sab ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath ye hadis bayan ki."
4159,"Aaraj ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya is zaat ki qism jiske hath mein Muhammad ki jaan hai! poori zamin par koi momin nahi magar main sab logon ki nisbat iske zyada qareeb hun, tum mein se jisne bhi jo qarz ya aulad chhodi (jiske zaaye honey ka dar hai) to main uska zimmedaar hun aur jisne maal chhoda wo usba (qaraabat daar jo kisi tarah bhi waaris bin sakta ho us) ka hai, wo jo bhi ho."
4160,"Hammam-bin-Munabba se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : ye wo hadisein hain jo hamein Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kin, phir unhon-ne chand hadisein bayan kin, unmein se ye bhi thi aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ki kitab ki ru se main mominon ke, (unki apni zaat samet) sab logon ki nisbat zyada qareeb hun, tum mein se jo qarz ya aulad chhod jaey to mujhey bulana mein uska wali hun aur jo maal chhod jaey to uske maal ke mamley main (zavil-furooz ke hissey dene ke baad) iske usba (qareeb tareen mard rishtedar) ko tarjeeh di jaey, wo jo bhi ho."
4161,"Muaz Anbari ne hamein hadis bayan ki : hamein Shoba ne Adi se hadis bayan ki ke unhon-ne abu-Hazim se suna, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : jisne maal chhoda wo iske waarison ka hai aur jisne bojh (be sahara aulad ho ya qarz) chhoda wo hamarey zimme hai."
4162,"(Muhammad-bin-Jafar) ghandar aur Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, magar ghandar ki hadis mein hai : jisne bojh chhoda uski zimme-dari maine ley li."
